description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 27, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 135, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and 3 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60275-56130-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [135 Votes, Top 15% Score]
